            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThe%20command%20of%20faith%20in%20the%20mouth%20of%20Jesus%20was%20astounding.%20With%20two%20words%2C%20an%20entire%20storm%20broke%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20of%20death%20was%20stilled.%20The%20Word%20of%20God%20in%20your%20mouth%20is%20the%20most%20powerful%20force%20in%20the%20world.%20Paul%20said%2C%20%22The%20message%20is%20close%20at%20hand%3B%20it%20is%20on%20your%20lips%20and%20in%20your%20heart%22%20(Romans%2010%3A8).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJesus%20is%20the%20Word%3B%20therefore%2C%20when%20you%20speak%20the%20Word%2C%20you%20are%20speaking%20Jesus%20into%20your%20situation.%20Faith%20consists%20of%20first%20believing%20in%20your%20heart%20that%20God's%20Word%20is%20true%20and%20then%20speaking%20that%20Word%20to%20your%20circumstances%20and%20watching%20them%20change.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20Jesus%20spoke%20the%20command%20of%20faith%20to%20the%20legion%20of%20demons%2C%20they%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20obey%20(Mark%205%3A13).%20The%20centurion%2C%20too%2C%20understood%20this%20principle%20and%20told%20the%20Lord%20that%20all%20that%20was%20needed%20was%20a%20simple%20command%20from%20His%20mouth%20for%20his%20servant%20to%20be%20healed%20(Matthew%208%3A8-9).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJoshua%20spoke%20to%20the%20sun%2C%20Jesus%20spoke%20to%20the%20fig%20tree%2C%20and%20you%20can%20speak%20to%20your%20storms.%20Expect%20the%20Word%20of%20God%20in%20your%20mouth%20to%20move%20mountains!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
