            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Leviticus.9:7-10:20",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ELeviticus%209%3A7-10%3A20%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_7%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20said%20to%20Aaron%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BCome%20to%20the%20altar%20and%20sacrifice%20your%20sin%20offering%20and%20your%20burnt%20offering%20to%20purify%20yourself%20and%20the%20people.%20Then%20present%20the%20offerings%20of%20the%20people%20to%20purify%20them%2C%20making%20them%20right%20with%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eto%20make%20atonement%20for%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20just%20as%20he%20has%20commanded.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_8%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Aaron%20went%20to%20the%20altar%20and%20slaughtered%20the%20calf%20as%20a%20sin%20offering%20for%20himself.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_9%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EHis%20sons%20brought%20him%20the%20blood%2C%20and%20he%20dipped%20his%20finger%20in%20it%20and%20put%20it%20on%20the%20horns%20of%20the%20altar.%20He%20poured%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20blood%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20altar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_10%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20burned%20on%20the%20altar%20the%20fat%2C%20the%20kidneys%2C%20and%20the%20long%20lobe%20of%20the%20liver%20from%20the%20sin%20offering%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20commanded%20Moses.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_11%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20meat%20and%20the%20hide%2C%20however%2C%20he%20burned%20outside%20the%20camp.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_12%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ENext%20Aaron%20slaughtered%20the%20animal%20for%20the%20burnt%20offering.%20His%20sons%20brought%20him%20the%20blood%2C%20and%20he%20splattered%20it%20against%20all%20sides%20of%20the%20altar.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_13%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20they%20handed%20him%20each%20piece%20of%20the%20burnt%20offering%2C%20including%20the%20head%2C%20and%20he%20burned%20them%20on%20the%20altar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_14%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20washed%20the%20internal%20organs%20and%20the%20legs%20and%20burned%20them%20on%20the%20altar%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20burnt%20offering.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_15%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ENext%20Aaron%20presented%20the%20offerings%20of%20the%20people.%20He%20slaughtered%20the%20people%26%23x2019%3Bs%20goat%20and%20presented%20it%20as%20an%20offering%20for%20their%20sin%2C%20just%20as%20he%20had%20first%20done%20with%20the%20offering%20for%20his%20own%20sin.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_16%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20presented%20the%20burnt%20offering%20and%20sacrificed%20it%20in%20the%20prescribed%20way.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_17%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20also%20presented%20the%20grain%20offering%2C%20burning%20a%20handful%20of%20the%20flour%20mixture%20on%20the%20altar%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20regular%20burnt%20offering%20for%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_18%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Aaron%20slaughtered%20the%20bull%20and%20the%20ram%20for%20the%20people%26%23x2019%3Bs%20peace%20offering.%20His%20sons%20brought%20him%20the%20blood%2C%20and%20he%20splattered%20it%20against%20all%20sides%20of%20the%20altar.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_19%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20took%20the%20fat%20of%20the%20bull%20and%20the%20ram%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20fat%20of%20the%20broad%20tail%20and%20from%20around%20the%20internal%20organs%26%23x2014%3Balong%20with%20the%20kidneys%20and%20the%20long%20lobes%20of%20the%20livers.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_20%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20placed%20these%20fat%20portions%20on%20top%20of%20the%20breasts%20of%20these%20animals%20and%20burned%20them%20on%20the%20altar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_21%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAaron%20then%20lifted%20up%20the%20breasts%20and%20right%20thighs%20as%20a%20special%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20just%20as%20Moses%20had%20commanded.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_22%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20that%2C%20Aaron%20raised%20his%20hands%20toward%20the%20people%20and%20blessed%20them.%20Then%2C%20after%20presenting%20the%20sin%20offering%2C%20the%20burnt%20offering%2C%20and%20the%20peace%20offering%2C%20he%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20altar.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_23%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%20went%20into%20the%20Tabernacle%2C%20and%20when%20they%20came%20back%20out%2C%20they%20blessed%20the%20people%20again%2C%20and%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20appeared%20to%20the%20whole%20community.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_9_24%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EFire%20blazed%20forth%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20presence%20and%20consumed%20the%20burnt%20offering%20and%20the%20fat%20on%20the%20altar.%20When%20the%20people%20saw%20this%2C%20they%20shouted%20with%20joy%20and%20fell%20face%20down%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_1%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ELeviticus%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Sin%20of%20Nadab%20and%20Abihu%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAaron%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons%20Nadab%20and%20Abihu%20put%20coals%20of%20fire%20in%20their%20incense%20burners%20and%20sprinkled%20incense%20over%20them.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20they%20disobeyed%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20by%20burning%20before%20him%20the%20wrong%20kind%20of%20fire%2C%20different%20than%20he%20had%20commanded.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_2%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20fire%20blazed%20forth%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20presence%20and%20burned%20them%20up%2C%20and%20they%20died%20there%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_3%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20said%20to%20Aaron%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20meant%20when%20he%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BI%20will%20display%20my%20holiness%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethrough%20those%20who%20come%20near%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20will%20display%20my%20glory%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebefore%20all%20the%20people.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3EAnd%20Aaron%20was%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_4%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20called%20for%20Mishael%20and%20Elzaphan%2C%20Aaron%26%23x2019%3Bs%20cousins%2C%20the%20sons%20of%20Aaron%26%23x2019%3Bs%20uncle%20Uzziel.%20He%20said%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BCome%20forward%20and%20carry%20away%20the%20bodies%20of%20your%20relatives%20from%20in%20front%20of%20the%20sanctuary%20to%20a%20place%20outside%20the%20camp.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_5%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20they%20came%20forward%20and%20picked%20them%20up%20by%20their%20garments%20and%20carried%20them%20out%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20just%20as%20Moses%20had%20commanded.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_6%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20said%20to%20Aaron%20and%20his%20sons%20Eleazar%20and%20Ithamar%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BDo%20not%20show%20grief%20by%20leaving%20your%20hair%20uncombed%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E10%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eby%20uncovering%20your%20heads.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20by%20tearing%20your%20clothes.%20If%20you%20do%2C%20you%20will%20die%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20anger%20will%20strike%20the%20whole%20community%20of%20Israel.%20However%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Israelites%2C%20your%20relatives%2C%20may%20mourn%20because%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20fiery%20destruction%20of%20Nadab%20and%20Abihu.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_7%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20you%20must%20not%20leave%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E10%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ETent%20of%20Meeting%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2010%3A9.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20you%20will%20die%2C%20for%20you%20have%20been%20anointed%20with%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20anointing%20oil.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20they%20did%20as%20Moses%20commanded.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_10_8%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%